@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title Command Dispatch Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Ui
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant Command
participant RecordList
participant Storage

User -> Ui: input command line
Ui -> Resumake: readCommand()
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: concrete Command
Resumake -> Command: execute(list)
Command -> RecordList: query/mutate
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare + write if changed
@enduml
